kpi.name: M5002C4

kpi_info.title: E-DCH DATA VOLUME FOR NON-SERVING CELL IN NON-SERVING E-DCH RLS UL
kpi_info.use: "Amount of MAC-e PDU data transferred in the E-DCH non-serving cell in the non-serving radiolink set in the uplink direction during the measurement interval. The MAC-e header includes to the MAC-e PDU data calculation.This counter is also used for MAC-i PDU data amount calculation.The MAC-i header includes to the MAC-i PDU data calculation."
